reviewText: Having dealt with kids all my life, this program was an eye opener for me. In my opinion, this program is for adults and older kids education and information. My 5 and 3 year old grandkids didn't quite get it. We will try something else. I gave it four stars because of the message imparted.

Very different from many of the other videos out there.  This one goes through mock kidnapings and abductions. I found it very useful. However, you might want to watch it on your own first before showing it to your kids.
